How to use the level editor
===========================

Running the editor
------------------

Run "python yva.py -e <levelname>

replacing <levelname> with the filename you want for your level. The level is
saved automatically when you exit the editor by pressing the Escape key.

Placing tiles
-------------

1. Click on a tile in the palette at the left of the screen.
2. Click inside the game where you want your tile.
3. Drag the mouse around for placing several tiles at once.

Growing and shrinking the level
-------------------------------

Press + to grow the level.
Press - to shrink the level.
